00:01:36.698 --> 00:01:39.033 position:10% line:5% align:start
I've been waiting for you...

00:01:39.067 --> 00:01:41.803 position:33% line:5% align:start
Fena Houtman.

00:01:41.836 --> 00:01:44.304 position:16% line:89% align:start
Who is that?

00:01:44.338 --> 00:01:45.974 position:61% line:89% align:start
Cody.

00:01:46.007 --> 00:01:47.909 position:38% line:89% align:start
What are you saying?

00:01:47.942 --> 00:01:49.276 position:35% line:89% align:start
In short...

00:01:49.309 --> 00:01:51.244 position:5% line:83% align:start
The various elements
that led you

00:01:51.278 --> 00:01:53.347 position:19% line:83% align:start
to standing
in this very place.

00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:57.250 position:44% line:83% align:start
Every one of them
was set into motion by us.

00:01:57.284 --> 00:02:00.722 position:50% line:77% align:start
For you see,
I am a part of Eden.

00:02:00.755 --> 00:02:02.624 position:21% line:83% align:start
And Eden
is a part of me.

00:02:02.657 --> 00:02:03.691 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:02:03.725 --> 00:02:07.160 position:7% line:83% align:start
It is we who govern
the bloodlines of the maidens.

00:02:07.194 --> 00:02:10.263 position:30% line:83% align:start
And guide them
to this place.

00:02:11.198 --> 00:02:13.601 position:10% line:83% align:start
Have you prepared
yourself?

00:02:13.635 --> 00:02:15.469 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:02:15.503 --> 00:02:21.475 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:27.147 position:24% line:89% align:start
What is this place?

00:02:28.883 --> 00:02:31.251 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru?

00:02:31.284 --> 00:02:33.688 position:38% line:77% align:start
Yukimaru?
Cody: This is the entrance.

00:02:36.791 --> 00:02:38.593 position:27% line:89% align:start
Cody.

00:02:40.128 --> 00:02:41.996 position:16% line:83% align:start
Where are we?
Where's Yukimaru?

00:02:42.030 --> 00:02:45.399 position:52% line:83% align:start
He is safe,
Fena La Pucelle Frederick.

00:02:45.432 --> 00:02:48.803 position:30% line:83% align:start
Princess, true daughter
of the king of England.

00:02:48.836 --> 00:02:50.505 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:02:50.538 --> 00:02:57.111 position:35% line:83% align:start
Also, the daughter of
Helena La Pucelle des Armoises.

00:02:57.145 --> 00:03:00.782 position:7% line:83% align:start
So you were the one
who guided me here?

00:03:00.815 --> 00:03:03.117 position:50% line:89% align:start
Not just me.

00:03:03.151 --> 00:03:05.218 position:16% line:83% align:start
The bread crumbs and visions
that led you

00:03:05.252 --> 00:03:08.790 position:27% line:83% align:start
on your quest trace back
to Jeanne La Pucelle...

00:03:08.823 --> 00:03:10.323 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:03:12.325 --> 00:03:14.996 position:35% line:83% align:start
...a distant ancestor
of yours.

00:03:15.029 --> 00:03:19.499 position:16% line:83% align:start
Memories from another maiden
that she handed down to you.

00:03:19.534 --> 00:03:24.172 position:41% line:83% align:start
Your fate -- proof
that this is your destiny.

00:03:24.204 --> 00:03:26.841 position:16% line:83% align:start
Every moment that's occurred
has been integral

00:03:26.874 --> 00:03:30.011 position:33% line:89% align:start
in weaving your story.

00:03:30.044 --> 00:03:32.113 position:7% line:89% align:start
And all of this...

00:03:32.146 --> 00:03:33.548 position:44% line:83% align:start
Is part of a test
to determine

00:03:33.581 --> 00:03:37.151 position:24% line:83% align:start
if you have what it takes
to be one of the maidens.

00:03:37.185 --> 00:03:39.654 position:35% line:83% align:start
You have demonstrated
that you do.

00:03:39.687 --> 00:03:42.657 position:27% line:83% align:start
You chose from the paths
we laid out in front of you,

00:03:42.690 --> 00:03:46.426 position:24% line:83% align:start
and the road you traveled
ultimately led you here.

00:03:50.631 --> 00:03:53.000 position:30% line:89% align:start
Fena: I chose?

00:03:53.034 --> 00:03:56.838 position:13% line:83% align:start
This whole time, my choices
were laid out for me.

00:03:58.039 --> 00:04:00.273 position:10% line:89% align:start
Like I was being controlled.

00:04:02.076 --> 00:04:04.045 position:21% line:83% align:start
What'll you force me
to do now?

00:04:04.078 --> 00:04:05.847 position:24% line:83% align:start
You want something,
don't you?

00:04:05.880 --> 00:04:07.648 position:33% line:89% align:start
Tell me what!

00:04:09.483 --> 00:04:11.418 position:5% line:89% align:start
We searched everywhere

00:04:11.451 --> 00:04:13.487 position:10% line:83% align:start
for a pure being
who could manage

00:04:13.521 --> 00:04:17.992 position:5% line:83% align:start
the ever-swelling number
of souls in our stead.

00:04:18.025 --> 00:04:20.161 position:30% line:89% align:start
We need to pick wisely.

00:04:20.194 --> 00:04:22.496 position:47% line:83% align:start
The chosen one
must test humanity,

00:04:22.530 --> 00:04:26.601 position:33% line:83% align:start
ascertain its maturity
and its worthiness.

00:04:26.634 --> 00:04:32.607 position:10% line:83% align:start
Cody: This is how The Maiden
of Choosing came to be.

00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:35.843 position:16% line:83% align:start
Through the countless cycles
of death and rebirth,

00:04:35.877 --> 00:04:38.813 position:41% line:83% align:start
they have continued
to make that choice.

00:04:40.982 --> 00:04:43.450 position:24% line:89% align:start
Fena: What choice?

00:04:43.483 --> 00:04:45.720 position:38% line:89% align:start
Death and rebirth...

00:04:45.753 --> 00:04:48.723 position:38% line:89% align:start
or its continuation.

00:04:48.756 --> 00:04:50.258 position:44% line:89% align:start
Cody: In short...

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:53.194 position:30% line:83% align:start
You may choose
to destroy the world...

00:04:53.227 --> 00:04:54.862 position:13% line:89% align:start
Or leave it be.

00:04:54.896 --> 00:04:56.164 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:04:56.197 --> 00:05:02.737 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:02.770 --> 00:05:05.139 position:10% line:89% align:start
That decision...

00:05:05.173 --> 00:05:06.741 position:16% line:83% align:start
that choice,
that is the reason

00:05:06.774 --> 00:05:10.343 position:10% line:83% align:start
why you were born
to be the Maiden of Choosing.

00:05:10.377 --> 00:05:13.214 position:47% line:83% align:start
[ Gasps ] Wait!
What are you saying?

00:05:13.247 --> 00:05:15.348 position:44% line:83% align:start
Destroy the world
or leave it?

00:05:15.382 --> 00:05:17.552 position:30% line:83% align:start
How can I possibly make
a choice like that?

00:05:17.585 --> 00:05:20.188 position:5% line:83% align:start
Will civilization's end
be today

00:05:20.221 --> 00:05:22.924 position:5% line:89% align:start
or in some unknown future?

00:05:22.957 --> 00:05:27.327 position:5% line:83% align:start
Your sole purpose here
is to make that decision.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:29.329 position:10% line:83% align:start
Franz: A maiden cannot shirk
her duty.

00:05:29.362 --> 00:05:33.100 position:19% line:89% align:start
A choice must be made.

00:05:33.134 --> 00:05:35.603 position:10% line:89% align:start
Now let us begin.

00:05:35.636 --> 00:05:41.309 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:41.341 --> 00:05:45.112 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Indistinct conversations ]

00:05:45.146 --> 00:05:47.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:51.619 position:38% line:89% align:start
No, stop!

00:05:51.652 --> 00:05:53.087 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it!

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:57.959 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:57.992 --> 00:05:59.994 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Exhales sharply ]

00:06:00.027 --> 00:06:04.832 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:04.866 --> 00:06:07.735 position:5% line:83% align:start
Franz: What we just showed you
is a portion of the past

00:06:07.768 --> 00:06:10.171 position:13% line:89% align:start
unknown to you.

00:06:10.204 --> 00:06:13.174 position:5% line:83% align:start
Mankind kills in order
to protect things,

00:06:13.207 --> 00:06:16.244 position:16% line:83% align:start
and competes
in order to survive.

00:06:16.277 --> 00:06:18.279 position:5% line:83% align:start
Cody: For now, everything's
held together

00:06:18.312 --> 00:06:20.147 position:5% line:89% align:start
in a precarious balance.

00:06:20.181 --> 00:06:22.717 position:13% line:83% align:start
But if this doesn't change,
the day will soon come

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:26.419 position:19% line:83% align:start
when all life on earth
will be extinguished.

00:06:26.453 --> 00:06:29.891 position:19% line:83% align:start
And the skies will turn
to darkness.

00:06:31.058 --> 00:06:33.027 position:47% line:89% align:start
That future --

00:06:33.060 --> 00:06:36.030 position:50% line:83% align:start
is it already
set in stone?

00:06:36.063 --> 00:06:38.199 position:41% line:83% align:start
Nothing
is set in stone.

00:06:38.232 --> 00:06:40.568 position:30% line:83% align:start
There are only
probabilities.

00:06:40.601 --> 00:06:45.740 position:5% line:83% align:start
We exist to make one probability
more likely than the others.

00:06:45.773 --> 00:06:49.610 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'll see.
This is one such example.

00:06:49.644 --> 00:06:54.181 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is a future that could
potentially await your friends.

00:06:54.215 --> 00:06:59.419 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:02.223 --> 00:07:07.427 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:10.298 --> 00:07:12.300 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:12.333 --> 00:07:18.773 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:18.806 --> 00:07:21.108 position:44% line:89% align:start
Guys?

00:07:21.142 --> 00:07:22.243 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru!

00:07:22.276 --> 00:07:24.045 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:07:24.078 --> 00:07:29.083 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:31.953 --> 00:07:33.354 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:33.387 --> 00:07:39.160 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:39.193 --> 00:07:44.999 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:45.032 --> 00:07:47.268 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Whimpering ]

00:07:47.301 --> 00:07:52.006 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:52.039 --> 00:07:55.876 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:55.910 --> 00:07:58.879 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Sobbing ]

00:08:00.348 --> 00:08:02.283 position:58% line:83% align:start
This is
your first option.

00:08:02.316 --> 00:08:03.651 position:47% line:89% align:start
Change nothing,

00:08:03.684 --> 00:08:06.821 position:13% line:83% align:start
and you let the sands of time
fall as they may.

00:08:09.390 --> 00:08:11.926 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Birds calling ]

00:08:20.134 --> 00:08:21.902 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru: Fena.

00:08:24.305 --> 00:08:26.807 position:55% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru.

00:08:26.841 --> 00:08:29.076 position:50% line:89% align:start
Where are we?

00:08:29.110 --> 00:08:33.014 position:5% line:83% align:start
A world that broke free
of the cycle of death.

00:08:33.047 --> 00:08:35.449 position:5% line:89% align:start
Leaving only hope behind,

00:08:35.483 --> 00:08:37.952 position:13% line:83% align:start
an Ark of Time
drifting aimlessly

00:08:37.985 --> 00:08:40.654 position:5% line:83% align:start
until the day of rebirth
arrives.

00:08:42.256 --> 00:08:44.725 position:13% line:83% align:start
When everything
will be reset.

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:45.559 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:08:45.593 --> 00:08:47.495 position:5% line:83% align:start
It will choose pure souls
at random

00:08:47.528 --> 00:08:49.663 position:5% line:89% align:start
to repopulate the earth

00:08:49.697 --> 00:08:53.502 position:5% line:83% align:start
and consign everything else
to oblivion.

00:08:53.534 --> 00:08:55.202 position:38% line:89% align:start
What does that mean?

00:08:55.236 --> 00:08:58.406 position:5% line:83% align:start
The old must be destroyed
to make way for the new.

00:08:58.439 --> 00:09:01.442 position:5% line:83% align:start
Only the wind, land,
and sea will remain.

00:09:01.475 --> 00:09:03.010 position:16% line:89% align:start
As well as...

00:09:03.044 --> 00:09:04.912 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:09:07.248 --> 00:09:09.817 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru?

00:09:11.018 --> 00:09:12.720 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you...

00:09:12.753 --> 00:09:14.121 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:09:16.490 --> 00:09:18.426 position:41% line:89% align:start
Your hand in mine.

00:09:18.459 --> 00:09:20.561 position:44% line:89% align:start
That was my vow.

00:09:20.594 --> 00:09:22.430 position:5% line:89% align:start
When maidens are reborn,

00:09:22.463 --> 00:09:24.398 position:5% line:83% align:start
the very first thing
she'll see --

00:09:24.432 --> 00:09:26.901 position:19% line:83% align:start
her beloved
by her side.

00:09:26.934 --> 00:09:30.671 position:5% line:77% align:start
The one who has been deemed
worthy of being her other half.

00:09:30.704 --> 00:09:33.808 position:7% line:83% align:start
[ Gasps ] But what will happen
to all the others?

00:09:33.841 --> 00:09:35.076 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ahh!

00:09:35.109 --> 00:09:41.282 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:41.315 --> 00:09:42.750 position:13% line:89% align:start
One last thing.

00:09:42.783 --> 00:09:44.785 position:7% line:83% align:start
Once you have made
your decision,

00:09:44.819 --> 00:09:48.789 position:5% line:83% align:start
you will have completed
your role as maiden.

00:09:48.823 --> 00:09:51.492 position:5% line:83% align:start
Cody: Maidens who have fulfilled
their purpose

00:09:51.526 --> 00:09:54.929 position:27% line:89% align:start
lose all their memories.

00:09:54.962 --> 00:09:55.863 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why?

00:09:55.896 --> 00:09:57.965 position:13% line:83% align:start
The human heart
is fragile.

00:09:57.998 --> 00:10:01.802 position:5% line:83% align:start
To destroy humanity or wait
and watch it be destroyed,

00:10:01.836 --> 00:10:04.839 position:5% line:83% align:start
her heart will break
no matter which she chooses.

00:10:04.872 --> 00:10:08.476 position:5% line:83% align:start
Anguish like that has
no place in Eden.

00:10:08.510 --> 00:10:09.677 position:47% line:89% align:start
It must go on.

00:10:09.710 --> 00:10:12.980 position:33% line:83% align:start
The future generations
of the maiden.

00:10:13.013 --> 00:10:16.951 position:5% line:83% align:start
Which means you'd need to
continue your sacred bloodline.

00:10:33.968 --> 00:10:36.637 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why does it have to be me?

00:10:36.670 --> 00:10:39.039 position:24% line:89% align:start
This is too cruel.

00:10:39.073 --> 00:10:40.741 position:44% line:89% align:start
It falls upon you

00:10:40.774 --> 00:10:43.644 position:41% line:83% align:start
because the choice
is your birthright.

00:10:45.547 --> 00:10:47.381 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't do it.

00:10:47.414 --> 00:10:49.551 position:16% line:89% align:start
I just can't.

00:10:49.584 --> 00:10:52.786 position:5% line:83% align:start
How could I possibly
make that choice?

00:10:57.458 --> 00:11:00.060 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ah. [ Gasps ]

00:11:05.466 --> 00:11:07.668 position:41% line:89% align:start
This is the moment.

00:11:07.701 --> 00:11:10.738 position:47% line:83% align:start
The very reason
that your heart beats.

00:11:11.472 --> 00:11:12.439 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Heart beating ]

00:11:12.473 --> 00:11:14.108 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:14.141 --> 00:11:15.809 position:5% line:83% align:start
You've called the shots
so far.

00:11:15.843 --> 00:11:18.245 position:7% line:83% align:start
And your gut hasn't
let us down yet.

00:11:18.279 --> 00:11:21.081 position:7% line:83% align:start
You can so do this,
Fena.

00:11:21.115 --> 00:11:22.651 position:58% line:89% align:start
Karin.

00:11:22.683 --> 00:11:24.718 position:13% line:89% align:start
Shitan: We've all seen it.

00:11:24.752 --> 00:11:28.455 position:5% line:83% align:start
You've gained all the experience
you need.

00:11:28.489 --> 00:11:30.324 position:19% line:83% align:start
So now you just choose!

00:11:30.357 --> 00:11:31.725 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yep, yep!Yep, yep!

00:11:31.759 --> 00:11:33.427 position:5% line:83% align:start
You gotta have faith
in yourself!

00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:34.795 position:47% line:83% align:start
I mean, you are
our fearless leader!

00:11:34.828 --> 00:11:38.199 position:5% line:77% align:start
You've got this!
You've got this!

00:11:38.232 --> 00:11:39.266 position:61% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:11:39.300 --> 00:11:40.267 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fena!

00:11:40.301 --> 00:11:41.268 position:27% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:11:41.302 --> 00:11:42.336 position:5% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:11:42.369 --> 00:11:43.437 position:80% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:11:43.470 --> 00:11:44.438 position:75% line:89% align:start
Fena!

00:11:44.471 --> 00:11:46.140 position:50% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:11:46.173 --> 00:11:47.474 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, Lady Fena!

00:11:47.509 --> 00:11:49.176 position:52% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena!

00:11:50.512 --> 00:11:53.113 position:30% line:89% align:start
Then I guess...

00:11:53.147 --> 00:11:54.516 position:30% line:89% align:start
I guess I'll...

00:11:54.549 --> 00:11:59.753 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:03.290 --> 00:12:08.295 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:15.336 --> 00:12:19.073 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:19.106 --> 00:12:20.441 position:27% line:89% align:start
Whoa!

00:12:20.474 --> 00:12:22.109 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's that?

00:12:22.142 --> 00:12:23.777 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Grunting ]

00:12:25.547 --> 00:12:26.814 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Indistinct shouting ]

00:12:26.847 --> 00:12:28.882 position:30% line:83% align:start
The whole place
is comin' down!

00:12:28.916 --> 00:12:31.553 position:58% line:83% align:start
Great.
Okay, what now?

00:12:31.586 --> 00:12:32.621 position:19% line:89% align:start
We retreat.

00:12:32.654 --> 00:12:33.887 position:38% line:83% align:start
But Fena
